title: (Fri Full) Kane Brown on his New Song Being Inspired 90s Country and His Favorite 90’s Country Artist + Amy Has Two Peculiar Airplane Observations
itunes:title: (Fri Full) Kane Brown on his New Song Being Inspired 90s Country and His Favorite 90’s Country Artist + Amy Has Two Peculiar Airplane Observations
description:
Kane Brown joins us to talk about his new song “Like I Love Country Music” and his Top 3 90’s country artist.  Amy shares two interesting observations she made flying back from LA on a flight without masks and that now serves alcohol.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
